properties.Name: EmployeeReview
properties.Description: A review of the employees performance in the associated Position(s).

Columns.Name: ReviewId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Review.

Columns.Name: EmployeeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Employee.

Columns.Name: UserID
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Position.

Columns.Name: ReviewDate
Columns.Description: The date of the job review.

Columns.Name: JobReviewRequestedByEmployeeIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the Job Review was requested by the employee.

Columns.Name: ReviewPeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The starting date for which the associated Employee Review is performed.

Columns.Name: ReviewPeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The ending date for which the associated Employee Review is performed.

Columns.Name: SalaryBeforeReview
Columns.Description: The employee's salary prior to the Job Review.

Columns.Name: SalaryAfterReview
Columns.Description: The employee's salary after the Job Review.

Columns.Name: MeritIncreaseAmount
Columns.Description: The amount awarded the employee in the form of a merit award.

Columns.Name: LengthOfServiceIncreaseAmount
Columns.Description: An amount awarded to an employee based upon length of service.

Columns.Name: TotalPossibleEvaluationCriteriaPoints
Columns.Description: The total number of points that may be achieved from the associated Evaluation Criteria in the current review.

Columns.Name: AchievedEvaluationCriteriaPoints
Columns.Description: The actual number of points achieved from the associated Evaluation Criteria in the current review.

Columns.Name: ReviewNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the employee review.

Columns.Name: GradeLevelClassificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Grade Level Classification.

Columns.Name: PreReviewTitleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the pre-review Title.

Columns.Name: PostReviewTitleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the pre-review Title.

Columns.Name: JobReviewTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Job Review Type.

Columns.Name: JobReviewClassificationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the job review classification.

Columns.Name: PreReviewPayGradeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Pay Grade.

Columns.Name: PostReviewPayGradeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Pay Grade.
